Subject: [PATCH 5/5] fix: replace #cfg(target_os=...) with
 moonbit_rt_get_random runtime FFI

- Remove #cfg(target_os=...) blocks (not supported by MoonBit compiler)
- Add unified rand_internal using moonbit_rt_get_random FFI
- Add patch file for MoonBit C runtime to add moonbit_rt_get_random
  with #ifdef _WIN32 guard selecting rand_s vs getentropy

This fixes the Windows CI linker error LNK2019 for getentropy.
